                     <interp inst="t18270215-54-person415" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Ramsey, of Liquorpond-street. On the 19th and 25th of January the prisoner pawned a Bible, a Prayer-book, and two Watts' Hymns.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270215-54-person416">
                  THOMAS 
                  REDPATH
               <interp inst="t18270215-54-person416" type="surname" value="REDPATH"></interp>
